{"tid":2318084,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚黃 招牌·秘制咖哩瀏覽飯 配奶茶紅豆冰","createTime":"2020-12-09T05:26:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T06:06:01.000Z","uid":302656,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"505179f03fa0a8f67dfeca288b5d502eed6d3330","tid":2318084,"uid":302656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/js8sLRq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjs8sLRq.png&h=bcca92e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KtM2zKW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKtM2zKW.png&h=606a505f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n痴撚線啊蕭生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有成十舊瀏覽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但啲飯太少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食曬啲飯都仲有一半咖哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講下個咖哩先<br />\n同街外嘅好唔同<br />\n好似有落番茄<br />\n食得出有好多香料<br />\n但杯奶茶紅豆冰就一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n茶味唔突出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只喺好似一杯變左色嘅紅豆冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3fcb5a7e3af82785aefd7b6f2c1b50cf8dd63af","tid":2318084,"uid":208973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:28:16.000Z","msg":"奶茶紅豆冰 睇字已經覺得伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4dfa057dc41d5c102e08b81c6e2cb9ce57141e","tid":2318084,"uid":274732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:33:54.000Z","msg":"有次我叫三眼仔小飯<br />\n啲飯仲比平時多左<br />\n埋單會員仲95折<br />\n小飯又平$1<br />\n下午茶時段又平幾蚊<br />\n好滿足棒住個肚走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：每個星期都會幫襯"},{"pid":"560039b8321226b8e1f96174327db9f4773a4367","tid":2318084,"uid":302656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"